I want that each constraint is expressed as a single property of the ff:kindergeldMainPersonShape. I want them to look like this:

    sh:property [
        sh:path ff:beruf_neu ;
        sh:minCount 1 ;
        sh:not [
            sh:in (ff:beruf_neu-ao-bfd ff:beruf_neu-ao-rente) ;
        ] ;
    ] ;
    sh:property [
        sh:path ff:einkommen_neu ;
        sh:minCount 1 ;
